summary: Adds two mead halls to the Whiterun area.
descriptionHtml:
This mod Simply adds a few NPCs, a Faction(There will be a quest to join it once I learn how to make/edit quests), and the Mead Halls. 
***********POSSIBLE SPOILER*****************
I plan to add a world space for the quest, probably just a duplicate of the \"Mind of Madness\" or \"Sovengarde\'. Also, it should be noted that these Mead Halls are duplicates of the Jorvasker Mead Hall and the Whiterun castle, as I liked both of them and wanted to make my own home in them.
This is my first mod, so please criticize the hell out of it. Nothing good came from baby-ing someone.
author: capngagi
